            <strong>Cathay FHC is committed to upholding our core values of “Integrity, Accountability, and Innovation”.</strong> And we align our business strategy with market conditions, leverage our financial competencies to achieve sustainable finance, drive digital transformation, and achieve group synergies with all subsidiaries together in order to provide better financial services and experiences that are comprehensive, convenient and personalized. Furthermore, we continue to complete our regional expansion and advance toward our vision of becoming a “leading financial institution in the Asia-Pacific region.”
        </p>
        <p class='cos-description' style="max-width:1200px">
            <strong>Cathay Financial Holdings (Cathay FHC) and its subsidiaries including Cathay Life Insurance, Cathay United Bank, Cathay Century Insurance, Cathay Securities, and Cathay Securities Investment Trust </strong>
